{"uid":"e4c9477132adc551","name":"test_context_budget_reflects_profile_max_tokens[10k_tokens]","fullName":"tests.ui.chat.test_context_management.TestContextManagementSettings#test_context_budget_reflects_profile_max_tokens","historyId":"ade8d65850f647c600a20b836139d3f5","time":{"start":1782455190571,"stop":1782455216101,"duration":25530},"description":"Context Budget panel in chat shows the max tokens set in profile.\n\n        Parameterized to verify:\n        - P1 (10,000 tokens): Standard value propagates correctly\n        - P2 (32,000 tokens): Updated value propagates (not cached)\n\n        Steps:\n            1. Navigate to profile settings.\n            2. Enable context management for new conversations.\n            3. Set Max Context Tokens to the parameterized value.\n            4. Navigate to chat and create a new conversation.\n            5. Send a short message to trigger Context Budget panel.\n            6. Verify the panel is visible.\n            7. Verify the max tokens displayed equals the configured value.\n\n        Cleanup: deletes the created conversation via API.\n        ","descriptionHtml":"<p>Context Budget panel in chat shows the max tokens set in profile.</p>\n<pre><code>    Parameterized to verify:\n    - P1 (10,000 tokens): Standard value propagates correctly\n    - P2 (32,000 tokens): Updated value propagates (not cached)\n\n    Steps:\n        1. Navigate to profile settings.\n        2. Enable context management for new conversations.\n        3. Set Max Context Tokens to the parameterized value.\n        4. Navigate to chat and create a new conversation.\n        5. Send a short message to trigger Context Budget panel.\n        6. Verify the panel is visible.\n        7. Verify the max tokens displayed equals the configured value.\n\n    Cleanup: deletes the created conversation via API.\n</code></pre>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":